  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Marketing              : Marketing management considerations of a company seeking to extend beyond its domestic market. Required changes in product, pricing, channel, and communications policies. Attention to international trade and export marketing in the Canadian context.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

